Text: RE Final Legislative Language Cc are awesome Many thanks Original Message From Delaney Hunter mailto Sent Tuesday July PM To Cc Barbara Barkovich Email Dominic DiMare Email Dorothy Rothrock Email John Fielder Email Phil Isenberg Email Jeff Dasovich Email Keith McCrea Email Linda Sherif Email Linda Sherif Email John White Email Mike Kahl Email Subject Final Legislative Language Rick Attached please find our final draft of legislative language per your request We are ready and willing to draft other sections or language as needed by you or the Speaker Please feel free to contact me if you have any questions about the draft Please note there are disagreements over two sections of language and they are so marked FYI I will be sending this document out to the entire Working Group for their information Thank you Delaney
